    "name": "猎虫者契约",
    "steam_appid": 3270580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎各位玩家加入官方QQ群：946824699</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord: rkdp2fr3qv</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注B站账号：ZYIGame</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘势力因为你的潜力，找上了你签订契约，希望你执行虫族猎杀任务，提供契约之力帮助你变强。你可以通过契约之力增加基本属性，也可以通过契约点购买道具、技能、弹药等，提升自己的战斗力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/a195a4aa152ebda6cf3beab291778423.poster.avif?t=1765600978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/a195a4aa152ebda6cf3beab291778423.webm?t=1765600978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/a195a4aa152ebda6cf3beab291778423.mp4?t=1765600978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1. 魔法战车+轻度背包管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没错，我们的主角是战车！威风凛凛的战车总能给我们更多的安全感，用武器和道具填满我们的装备格子，向敌人尽情地倾泻你的火力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一点要注意的是，我们的游戏需要更多地关注<strong>构筑策略</strong>，比如在有限的装备格子中怎么样搭配才能有更舒适地战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/25d867b609e0e264fecd6dac0458533c.avif?t=1765600978\" width=1560 height=872 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/925da94222e9e3e21796be813b6968af.avif?t=1765600978\" width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2. 类“爬塔”式路线选择</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了增加更多的<strong>策略性</strong>，我们增加了<strong>路线图</strong>玩法。你既可以选择<strong>精英</strong>更多的路线，<strong>挑战更高难度</strong>的同时赚取更多的经济；也可以选择<strong>奇遇、宝藏</strong>更多的路线，<strong>减少战斗</strong>的同时<strong>靠运气</strong>获得更多资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/f52b7acacc6fb8ff6e73b105e442b23d.avif?t=1765600978\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3. 丰富的合成配方</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了可以直接购买更高阶的物品外，你还可以通过消耗 2~4 个低阶物品进行<strong>合成</strong>！此外，你还可以通过<strong>异变符文</strong>靠运气直接变化出更高阶的物品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/78caf6d0d1f84231e2408176776b1fac.avif?t=1765600978\" width=1560 height=860 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4. 深度构筑策略</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过合理的搭配可以构筑出伤害爆炸而且火力无限的<strong>无尽雷球流派！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/bdfe4c9163faf156622b787a6540d0b1.poster.avif?t=1765600978\" width=648 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/bdfe4c9163faf156622b787a6540d0b1.webm?t=1765600978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/bdfe4c9163faf156622b787a6540d0b1.mp4?t=1765600978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/3c6122980236ba879bdea23ec02f2926.poster.avif?t=1765600978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/3c6122980236ba879bdea23ec02f2926.webm?t=1765600978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270580/extras/3c6122980236ba879bdea23ec02f2926.mp4?t=1765600978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
